# Trained model artifacts. Anchored to repo root so this doesn't also ignore
# src/foryou/db/models. The serving artifact is committed and baked into the
# production image: the deployed API has no training path, and default_scorer()
# falls back to the heuristic *silently* if the file is missing. Ignore the
# directory's contents, not the directory, so the negation below can apply.
/models/*
!/models/scoring_model.json

